# MASTER BLUEPRINT: ISO 27001 ISMS

## Architecture Overview
- **Pattern**: Modular Monolith / Hexagonal
- **Stack**: React (Front) + Express (Back) + MySQL (DB)
- **Monorepo**: Root package.json managing workspaces.

## Data Schema (Sequelize)
- **Document**: id(PK), name, category, status(Enum), responsible, deadline, mandatory(Bool).
- **Control**: id(PK), controlId, name, category(Enum), status(Enum), justification, evidence.
- **Audit**: id(PK), type, date, status(Enum), auditor, findings.
- **NonConformity**: id(PK), type(Enum), description, control, status(Enum), deadline.

## Privilegios Engine (RBAC)
- **Models**: Role, Permission, User, RolePermissions (Through).
- **Middleware**: `checkPermission(resource, action)`
- **Standard Roles**: `admin`, `auditor`, `editor`, `viewer`.

## UI Design Tokens
- **Theme**: Premium Blue / Slate
- **Layout**: Sidebar Navigation + Gradient Header
- **KPIs**: Progress %, Docs count, Controls coverage, Open NCs.

## API Specification
- Base: `/api`
- Docs: `/api/documents` [GET, POST, PUT, DELETE]
- Controls: `/api/controls` [GET, POST, PUT]
- Audits: `/api/audits` [GET, POST, PUT]
- NCs: `/api/nonconformities` [GET, POST, PUT, DELETE]
- Documentation: `/api-docs` (Swagger)
